I understand, Kay.  As I mentioned earlier, ordinarily I would just send a private message 
to people on eBay when I saw something crazy going on, but about 2 weeks ago 
(guessing) eBay disabled the ability for anyone but the seller to contact bidders, due to all 
the scammers out there trying to rip off people.  

Kind of a bummer, but as a buyer, I appreciate the protection, as I&#39;ve received many bogus 
offers in the past and found it quite annoying.  

I&#39;ve never sold anything on eBay, or Craigslist, so don&#39;t know the ins and outs of it all.  I&#39;ll 
leave that up to you experienced folks to list whatever, if that is what you choose to do.  If 
not, that&#39;s OK too!  :-)

Margaret  

